<p>Artificial intelligence is reshaping the design landscape. In 2026, AI design tools can generate stunning visuals from text prompts, convert hand-drawn wireframes into polished mockups, remove backgrounds with one click, and maintain brand consistency across hundreds of assets — often at a fraction of the cost of traditional software. We evaluated nine of the leading AI design tools across image generation, UI/UX prototyping, vector design, photo editing, and brand design. Here are our top picks to supercharge your creative workflow.</p>

